(51, 'acid', 'poison', 40, 100, 30, 'special', 'all-opponents', 0, 'Opposing Pokémon are attacked with a spray of harsh acid. This may also lower their Sp. Def stats.', 'Has a $effect_chance% chance to lower the target''s Special Defense by one stage.'),
